  "detailed_description": "'Cargo Duty' is a goofy horror resource management game. Keep an eye on your ship and don't let any creatures in.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCargo Duty is a multiplayer game up to 6 players. You and your friends go from moon to moon collecting cargo. There are creatures that will try and stop you. Use the countermeasures on the ship to get rid of any unwanted attention.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHow long will you survive ?",
